#: ../../faq.rst:860
# b45f866412d84206bf93ee7d40be67f6
msgid "Downloading from the Internet can sometimes result in a corrupted download. If the |app| installer you downloaded is not opening, try downloading it again. If re-downloading it does not work, download it from `an alternate location <http://sourceforge.net/projects/calibre/files/>`_. If the installer still doesn't work, then something on your computer is preventing it from running."
